gov.usgs.volcanoes.winston.server.wws

Class WwsCommandString

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.volcanoes.winston.server.wws.WwsCommandString

  • public class WwsCommandString
extends Object
    A convenience class for dealing with WWS commands. fields are separated by a single space position 0: command optionally followed by a colon position 1: id positions 2 through 4: SCN positions 2 through 5: SCNL position 5 or 6: start time position 6 or 7: end time
    Author:
    Dan Cervelli
